{"tid":1530494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中英聯合聲明的謬誤? 召喚法律撚","createTime":"2019-09-02T03:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T08:48:53.000Z","uid":261544,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ce60970470018d335cd4daa5d27ef0a5d8e042c8","tid":1530494,"uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:30:10.000Z","msg":"岩岩同另一個bro在以下呢篇討論的時候<br />\n<br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n諗到一樣野<br />\n(btw, 樓主唔好意思，騎劫左你個post,最多我錫你春袋補數)<br />\n<br />\n本身中英聯合聲明需要兩種語言去解釋地雙方聽呢份聲明嘅合法性同重要性<br />\n然而究竟言語上嘅翻譯，<br />\n可唔可以完全表達到份聲明所有意思，清，無誤地俾雙方聽呢?<br />\n<br />\n因為其中最大嘅謬誤就係，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">中國外交部聲稱呢份聲明係一份歷史文件</span></span><br />\n而<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">G7嗰度講道明,中英聯合聲明仍然係一份有效嘅合約</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n咁係咪應該要研究下呢份聲明嘅重要性同是否仍有效?<br />\n<br />\nif 份合約本身因為言語上的錯誤，<br />\n令到雙方有誤會<br />\n咁呢份聲明應該廢除<br />\n亦即係話香港仍然屬於英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但如果中國承認 中英聯合聲明合法性同重要性， 咁佢就必須要比香港有真普選<br />\n而 期限就係&lt;香港人權及民主法案&gt;所講嘅2020年<br />\n<br />\n對我哋嚟講係雙贏嘅局面"},{"pid":"060dfa186e634822a3b4f7fd253344f73f6d91a1","tid":1530494,"uid":7948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ALupoHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FALupoHa.jpg&h=b51370df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abdafeb9f3ed99bb76868c15f4f5753946adfec3","tid":1530494,"uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:32:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"69a1802798f0e8ec4d71eae8a9365ea3d44a3bef","tid":1530494,"uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":